{"tid":2356994,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"黃宗澤與內地網紅食飯照流出，網民猜測佢會係下一個郭富城？","createTime":"2021-01-07T06:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T07:14:50.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"415b2843fa989150630779dfd48f09be5cb2f6db","tid":2356994,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T06:42:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/kWK01hLVPVCViIQuHLUE4Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEyODAuODg4ODg4ODg4ODg5/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-01/c4f36da0-509c-11eb-9f1e-da8dd2dbd119\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FkWK01hLVPVCViIQuHLUE4Q--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEyODAuODg4ODg4ODg4ODg5%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-01%2Fc4f36da0-509c-11eb-9f1e-da8dd2dbd119&h=ad74e077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地網紅「方禾齊」與黃宗澤食飯<br />\n黃宗澤（Bosco）自同胡杏兒分手後，緋聞一直冇停過，先有緋聞女友陳嘉桓，又有內地女友張沙沙，更傳出曾力追余香凝，總之佢嘅感情世界係錯綜複雜。近日內地網紅「方禾齊」喺小紅書上載與黃宗澤食晚飯嘅照片，並留言讚佢靚仔：「太開心了哈哈哈，黃宗澤是真的老痞帥了！！！從小看TVB就特別愛看黃宗澤的戲，他一開口我們就感覺自己穿越到港劇裡了。（把他臉拍胖了哈哈，本人一點都不胖！）是真的帥啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊」<br />\n<br />\n相片中嘅黄宗澤臉上保持微笑，不過表情就有啲緊張同生硬。佢戴上黑色鴨舌帽及身穿白色T恤，與6位美女合照，真係艷福無邊呀！相片流出後，唔少網民都估佢會唔會係下一個郭富城，與內地網紅結婚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/EjV_A1NDhN7Rto7hS0PIEg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-01/ce136570-509c-11eb-bf75-a23090a67f36\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FEjV_A1NDhN7Rto7hS0PIEg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-01%2Fce136570-509c-11eb-bf75-a23090a67f36&h=3f7e7c3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/hO09MS_JRM6Nkmy0CXChsg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-01/deed3560-509c-11eb-bedf-4c37311d7a48\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FhO09MS_JRM6Nkmy0CXChsg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-01%2Fdeed3560-509c-11eb-bedf-4c37311d7a48&h=63bb896a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Bt5apJYh4yVsVOeNwIwbYg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOS4xMTExMTExMTExMTEx/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-01/58abbc00-508e-11eb-afff-af51886c9e60\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FBt5apJYh4yVsVOeNwIwbYg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOS4xMTExMTExMTExMTEx%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-01%2F58abbc00-508e-11eb-afff-af51886c9e60&h=965e44dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f564d139aa6e037117d3a6f5f454b54a0433f179","tid":2356994,"uid":124655,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T06:47:42.000Z","msg":"黃色衫條女叫咩名"},{"pid":"60e7efd41452c2c793fc6d675f05105f790e0cde","tid":2356994,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T06:48:58.000Z","msg":"有無唔P圖版"},{"pid":"1141dfaf99b6ba2b5a37d78304f0811c0e7d30c1","tid":2356994,"uid":61414,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T06:52:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲女唔多掂啵"},{"pid":"91771a216608928394feda6781205443fcac6083","tid":2356994,"uid":117894,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T06:54:19.000Z","msg":"老痞帥係讚美來？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d718ba35ac6df4820f19d96f6a6dc7ea4adf29b0","tid":2356994,"uid":127425,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:03:42.000Z","msg":"咁正同成班女女玩7P<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wai